rong>殘體</strong></span>注意<br />\n<a href=\"http://hw.gamekee.com/61339.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhw.gamekee.com%2F61339.html&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpBIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=eee602d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hw.gamekee.com/61339.html</a><br />\n專武記住要傳說(紅色) 唔洗理佢入便幅圖既顏色<br />\n因為要傳說先有特殊能力<br />\n有心機刷既要留意件裝既主屬同套裝效果<br />\n最好配合返隻角色既定位<br />\n後面30抽係指有30次機會既10抽<br />\nNEXT左就無得返轉頭<br />\n角色技能卡推薦塔拉<br />\n或者可以參考下以下PVP/Tier List<br />\n韓服PVP TOP50<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=39349&amp;snA=19&amp;tnum=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D39349%26snA%3D19%26tnum%3D1&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpBIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=17c3b89c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=39349&amp;snA=19&amp;tnum=1</a><br />\n韓服Tier List<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=39349&amp;snA=7&amp;tnum=7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D39349%26snA%3D7%26tnum%3D7&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpBIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=610a2110\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=39349&amp;snA=7&amp;tnum=7</a><br />\n外國Tier List<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gacha.gg/guides/heroes-war-counterattack-tier-list/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gacha.gg%2Fguides%2Fheroes-war-counterattack-tier-list%2F&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpBIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=46a37676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gacha.gg/guides/heroes-war-counterattack-tier-list/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"blue\">新手上路</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=39349&amp;snA=20&amp;tnum=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D39349%26snA%3D20%26tnum%3D2&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpBIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=8598342b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=39349&amp;snA=20&amp;tnum=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"blue\">裝備篇</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1jpWkbm4q8E&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=350\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1jpWkbm4q8E%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D350&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpBIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=93719b3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1jpWkbm4q8E&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=350</a><br />\n<br />\n裝分主屬同副屬<br />\n星數 - 主屬數值<br />\n顏色 - 一開始有幾多項副屬 (紅 = 4, 紫 = 3, 藍 = 2, 綠 = 1)<br />\n仲有一項係主副屬中間應該就係隨機出<br />\n<br />\n武器/防具/腰帶係固定主屬<br />\n拳套/戒指/戰靴係隨機主屬<br />\n武器 - 攻實數(flat)<br />\n拳套 - 攻血防%/實數/攻速<br />\n防具 - 防實數<br />\n戒指 - 攻血防%/實數/暴/暴傷/貫<br />\n皮帶 - 血實數<br />\n戰靴 - 攻血防%/實數/命中/抵抗<br />\n副屬以上全部都有機會出現<br />\n同埋就算同星同色都有個range<br />\n例如5*紫裝+0 攻擊力係可以3-6%<br />\n星數同顏色對副屬個數值有無影響未睇得出<br />\n暫時睇落星數有好細既分別/顏色無影響<br />\n<br />\n以下只為外國youtuber建議<br />\n經實際測試後<br />\n由於%係只計算基本能力 額外加成既flat能力係唔計<br />\n即係例如你隻角色1000+1000攻<br />\n再裝件+10%攻既裝上去<br />\n會係1000+1100攻 而唔係1000+1200攻<br />\n所以%裝要到一定練度先會跑贏flat<br />\n以攻擊為例<br />\n5* +15分別係490同51%<br />\n即係大約要去到1000基攻 %先跑得贏flat<br />\n而呢個數值大約需要角色~40lv 能力強化到SS-SSS<br />\n當然實際都要再睇角色啦<br />\n<br />\nDPS:<br />\n套裝<br />\n鬥魂4+突襲2<br />\n猛攻4+突襲2<br />\n疾走4+突襲2<br />\n主屬<br />\n拳套 - 攻%/攻速<br />\n戒指 - 暴/暴傷/攻%<br />\n戰靴 - 攻%<br />\n副屬<br />\n攻%/暴/暴傷/攻速<br />\n<br />\nSupport:<br />\n套裝<br />\n生存6<br />\n疾走4+生存2<br />\n主屬<br />\n拳套 - 攻速<br />\n戒指 - 血%<br />\n戰靴 - 血%/命中<br />\n副屬<br />\n攻速/血%/防%/命中<br />\n<br />\nTank:<br />\n套裝<br />\n生存/剛毅<br />\n主屬<br />\n拳套 - 血%/防%<br />\n戒指 - 血%/防%<br />\n戰靴 - 血%/防%/抵抗<br />\n副屬<br />\n攻速/血%/防%/抵抗<br />\n<br />\n屬性/套裝部分只係大約概念<br />\n唔一定死跟<br />\n例如有韓仔樹妖11階係用掠奪裝(只可以用pvp幣買)<br />\nsupport為左cleanse可能都會用命中裝之類<br />\n<br />\n另外建議初期裝備星數優先<br />\n副屬太隨機同埋+3/6/9/12先跳 (+15唔會跳副屬 但+14&gt;+15主屬會倍增)<br />\n始終暫時仲係開荒期 資源有限<br />\n主要以最少資源打到高層數裝副本優先<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"blue\">其他攻略</span></strong><br />\n戰鬥中心點升<br />\n<a href=\"https://cafe.naver.com/com2usheroeswar/9924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcafe.naver.com%2Fcom2usheroeswar%2F9924&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpBIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=e3672253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cafe.naver.com/com2usheroeswar/9924</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ydCLrej.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FydCLrej.png&h=9c9c831e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樹妖11階<br />\n<a href=\"https://cafe.naver.com/com2usheroeswar/8719\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcafe.naver.com%2Fcom2usheroeswar%2F8719&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpBIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=9592a6fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cafe.naver.com/com2usheroeswar/8719</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IbM1pv3ecTM&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIbM1pv3ecTM%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpBIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=79cce9f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IbM1pv3ecTM&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n</p>"},{"pid":"f4643528ac5661ef4c2a1a781df6cf89f0559f62","tid":2302608,"uid":180851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7373094724db977fa3936dfb249caaf235fdabb","tid":2302608,"uid":30839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:04:03.000Z","msg":"重覆左<br />\n請移玉步到湯巴POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2302594/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2302594/page/1</a>"}]}